      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated midnight metallic paint that retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, light scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but cared for. Inside, the cabin remains in impressive shape; the leather-trimmed seats show minimal bolster wear and are free of any punctures or thinning. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, operates exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine is clean and performs flawlessly, benefiting from a lifetime of synthetic oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The transmission shifts are crisp and seamless, and the suspension remains tight, providing a quiet and composed ride over varied surfaces. We have recently fitted a fresh set of all-season tires and replaced the brake pads, so there are no immediate maintenance needs. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept vehicle that comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys. It is a dependable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking luxury without the new-car price tag.",
